  "texts": [
    "For students, the worries focussed particularly on the unreliability of information it produced, fear of being accused of plagiarism if they used it and a concern about growing dependence on technology.",
    "While often its use was claimed to be justified for its time and stress reduction this may have underestimated the overall impact on learning.",
    "Saving time on learning tasks may unintentionally remove significant opportunities to learn.",
    "Many of the deeper ethical and societal issues such as around the exploitative way ChatGPT was developed were not fully understood.",
    "Yet it was clear that how writing was done digitally had become controversial."
